text: Frank Dobson (born 11 June 1934) is a British former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:British male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Great Britain Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from New Malden Category:Sportspeople from London
